Unicron/Vehement/Teufel:




Unicron remained working on Teufel via the computer and did not respond to 
Vehement's speach.

The Archbishop of the Brotherhood had tried speaking with Unicron for several 
cycles with no results.  He sighed his head, only having ingested 87% of the 
knowledge he'd downloaded from the Guardian computer.  He continued to stand 
and try and make sense of the information.
